					<description><![CDATA[<p>Researchers are leading the nation in using powerful and precise radioactive drugs to treat people with complex cancers. &amp;#160; ROCHESTER, Minn. — Mayo Clinic has treated the first person in the U.S. using a novel radioactive medicine for advanced breast cancer as part of an international multisite clinical trial. The medicine used in this clinical [&amp;#8230;]</p>
